import React from 'react'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; const Home = () => { return (
{/* Hero Section */}

AI-Powered Medical Diagnosis
Made Simple

Advanced artificial intelligence meets healthcare to provide instant, accurate analysis of skin lesions, chest X-rays, and virtual triage assessments. Trusted by healthcare professionals worldwide.

Get Started Learn More
{/* Features Section */}

Comprehensive Medical AI Suite

Three powerful AI modules working together to provide accurate, fast, and reliable medical analysis and guidance.

{/* Skin Analysis Feature */}

Skin Cancer Detection

Advanced ISIC-trained ResNet-50 model analyzes skin lesions for 7 different conditions including melanoma, basal cell carcinoma, and benign lesions with 95%+ accuracy.

ABCDE Analysis (Asymmetry, Border, Color, Diameter, Evolution)
Visual overlays and heatmaps
Personalized recommendations
Analyze Skin Lesion
{/* Radiology Feature */}

Radiology Analysis

CheXNet DenseNet-121 powered analysis of chest X-rays and CT scans, detecting 14 different pathologies including pneumonia, pneumothorax, and cardiomegaly.

Multi-label pathology detection
Urgency level assessment
DICOM format support
Upload X-ray/CT
{/* Triage Feature */}

Virtual Triage Assistant

AI-powered symptom analysis using Groq and medical knowledge bases to provide intelligent triage assessment and personalized medical guidance.

Natural language processing
Urgency level determination
24/7 availability
Start Triage Chat
{/* Stats Section */}

Trusted by Healthcare Professionals

Our AI models are trained on millions of medical images and validated by medical experts

95%+
Diagnostic Accuracy
2.5M+
Images Analyzed
50K+
Healthcare Users
24/7
Availability
{/* How It Works Section */}

How It Works

Get medical insights in three simple steps using our advanced AI technology

1

Upload & Describe

Upload your medical image or describe your symptoms using our secure, HIPAA-compliant platform.

2

AI Analysis

Our advanced AI models analyze your data using state-of-the-art deep learning algorithms trained on millions of medical cases.

3

Get Results

Receive detailed analysis results with visual overlays, confidence scores, and personalized recommendations within seconds.

{/* CTA Section */}

Ready to Experience AI-Powered Healthcare?

Join thousands of healthcare professionals who trust MediScan-AI for accurate, fast, and reliable medical analysis.

Start Free Analysis View Documentation
); }; export default Home;
